死難者國家公祭日。</span><br />\n<br />\n14億同胞，再一次，<br />\n<br />\n以國之名，<br />\n<br />\n祭民族之殤。<br />\n<br />\n又一次站在歷史與現實的交匯點，<br />\n<br />\n83年前的那場腥風血雨，<br />\n<br />\n何曾忘？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs1.huanqiucdn.cn/dp/api/files/imageDir/593572e8fd244194adcf57890c10f17e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs1.huanqiucdn.cn%2Fdp%2Fapi%2Ffiles%2FimageDir%2F593572e8fd244194adcf57890c10f17e.png&h=0c688a53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs1.huanqiucdn.cn/dp/api/files/imageDir/730000844c02fa61527b1091b7a4c281.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs1.huanqiucdn.cn%2Fdp%2Fapi%2Ffiles%2FimageDir%2F730000844c02fa61527b1091b7a4c281.jpg&h=7e64aa72&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T03:36:01.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"xx-large\">人民不犠牲 國家怎發展 <br />\n<br />\n支持黨 支持人民犠牲 <br />\n<br />\n感謝外國入侵令國家意識到落後</span></span>"},{"pid":"e8ba9031a39efd64e0b57190e5e3efd93cc8b71d","tid":2323094,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe55fa11186ab3d47052fac6db3e382c986c3219","tid":2323094,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a328aed16cbf99ee21a37c688229488fd8e42b61","tid":2323094,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T01:54:12.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">永不消逝的南京記憶：走過至暗時刻，他們仍在守護和平</span></strong><br />\n來源：中國新聞網<br />\n<br />\n2020-12-13 07:02<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">中新網12月13日電(甘甜) 今天，是第七個南京大屠殺死難者國家公祭日。</span><br />\n<br />\n14億同胞，再一次，<br />\n<br />\n以國之名，<br />\n<br />\n祭民族之殤。<br />\n<br />\n又一次站在歷史與現實的交匯點，<br />\n<br />\n83年前的那場腥風血雨，<br />\n<br />\n何曾忘？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs1.huanqiucdn.cn/dp/api/files/imageDir/593572e8fd244194adcf57890c10f17e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs1.huanqiucdn.cn%2Fdp%2Fapi%2Ffiles%2FimageDir%2F593572e8fd244194adcf57890c10f17e.png&h=0c688a53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"htt